 of directors of eli lilly and company in  a native of straughn indiana he received a bachelor’s degree in economics from depauw university in  and his mba in finance and real estate from indiana university in  he also completed the advanced management program at harvard university graduate school of business boston in  hoover was the chairman president and chief executive officer of ball corporation from april  until january  having been elected president and chief executive officer in january  he was chairman and chief executive officer until january  hoover joined ball corporation in  during his career he has served as vice president finance and administration of both the company’s agricultural systems division and the company’s aerospace systems group he was elected vice president and treasurer in  and senior vice president and chief financial officer in  he was named executive vice president and elected to the company’s board of directors in  in  he was elected vice chairman in addition to the role of chief financial officer hoover became president of ball corporation in january  and was named chief operating officer in april  hoover is a member of the boards of ball corporation energizer holdings inc and steelcase inc he is a member of the board of the national association of manufacturers and is a member and past chair of the board of governors of the can manufacturers institute cmi hoover is a member and past chair of the board of trustees of depauw university and on the indiana university kelley school of business dean’s council he is also a director of boulder community hospital children’s hospital colorado and a member of the colorado forum he also served on the boards of irwin financial corporation and qwest international inc r david hoover  executive bio compensation history and contacts  equilar atlas   log in  sign up x   as featured in r david hoover board member at ball corporation view full profile are you r david hoover claim your profile   sign u